Comment: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:13.85,ED2,,0,0,0,,ROCKET THRUSTER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.79,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você se sente sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.58,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Você consegue me ouvir agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:53.13,OPL2,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\3c&H000000&\pos(960,1050)}Sua mente está tão longe, ainda na Terra
